===Radiation outside primary containment of the reactors===
Outside the primary containment, plant radiation-level measurements have also varied significantly.

On 25 March, an analysis of stagnant water in the basement floor of the turbine building of Unit 1 showed heavy contamination.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nisa.meti.go.jp/english/files/en20110325-6.pdf |title=Regarding the result of concentration measurement in the stagnant water on the basement floor of the turbine building of Unit 1 of Fukushima Dai-ichi Nuclear Power Station |accessdate=26 March 2011 }}</ref>
