| Seawater (at discharge) || 0.04 || Bq/mL (iodine-131) ||<ref name=tepco28>{{cite web|url=http://www.tepco.co.jp/en/press/corp-com/release/betu11_e/images/110328e3.pdf|title=The result of nuclide analysis of seawater|work=TEPCO|date=28 March 2011}}</ref> ||
|-
|  Seawater (at discharge) ||0.09 || Bq/mL (caesium-137) ||<ref name=tepco28/> ||
|-
|  drinking water ||0.1 || Bq/g (iodine-131) ||<ref name=IAEAiodine/> ||
|-
